data.description: Experience the fusion of prime location and modern elegance with this stunning home, serenely nestled near the pulsing heart of Osceola Pkway, US 192, 535, 417, the Turnpike, and I-4. With proximity that puts shopping centers, coveted dining spots, the enchanting Disney Spring, and many local attractions at your fingertips, convenience is yours to claim.    This home isn't just a place—it's a statement. Immaculately maintained and boasting a distinctive charm, this dwelling offers three plush bedrooms and two-and-a-half luxurious bathrooms. The dual-car garage is a testament to practicality, while the open-concept floor plan radiates a spacious ambiance that whispers 'welcome home.'    Step into an inviting foyer that seamlessly flows into the living space with premium ceramic tiles. The exception is the lovely bedrooms; these havens of rest embrace you with warm, plush carpeting underfoot.    The kitchen is a gourmet's dream. Quartz countertops lend the island a sleek, modern aesthetic, complemented by the shimmer of top-notch stainless appliances. A built-in bar enhances the space, making it as functional as beautiful.    Venture outside to discover your private oasis—a fenced backyard perfect for family fun and entertainment. The outdoor kitchen top invites you to play host, setting the stage for memorable evenings under the stars.    The sprawling master suite promises sanctuary and comfort. The attached bathroom pampers with its roomy walk-in shower and double vanity, while the generously sized walk-in closet caters to all your storage needs.    For those who seek more than a home, the Hideaway Club and the newly minted Bronson Club await an abundance of amenities. From a state-of-the-art fitness center and a beautiful resort-style swimming pool to a full-service restaurant and bar, these are more than mere conveniences—they're extensions of your living space.    Make this spectacular residence yours and embrace a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and sophistication.
